commit 3a95473fc73e2c0b3c099b34c8fa962870803981
Author: Jackson Atassi <jackson.atassi@outlook.com>
Date:   Sun Jul 5 11:36:19 2026 -0400

    worktree-parallelism: trivial-merge relaxation — compose-and-prove at every merge point
    
    Deletes the unordered-overlap plan-check error (footprint disjointness becomes
    plan-agent bias, not lint law) and replaces the conflicts-impossible posture at
    every merge point (build's sibling merge, validate's integration merge and
    publish-rebase) with compose-and-prove: resolve a textual conflict only with a
    resolution serving both sides' stated intents, proven by the merged suite going
    green; otherwise blocked naming the conflicting paths (ADR-0042).

